n face"},{"s":88.16,"e":89.04,"text":"But the room stays warm"},{"s":89.04,"e":90.02,"text":"When the tray rolls through"},{"s":90.02,"e":90.92,"text":"Everybody need"},{"s":90.92,"e":91.62,"text":"Something true"},{"s":91.62,"e":93.18,"text":"And we all come in"},{"s":93.18,"e":94.78,"text":"With a cracked-up grin"},{"s":94.78,"e":96.56,"text":"Little bit of sin"},{"s":96.92,"e":98.32,"text":"Little bit of skin"},{"s":98.32,"e":100.02,"text":"Little bit of hope"},{"s":100.02,"e":101.68,"text":"In a paper cup"},{"s":101.68,"e":103.26,"text":"Say a small amen"},{"s":103.26,"e":106.48,"text":"When the bowl fills up"},{"s":106.48,"e":109.7,"text":"St John’s plate, keep me alive"},{"s":109.7,"e":112.92,"text":"St John’s plate, let me survive"},{"s":112.92,"e":116.54,"text":"Under God’s sky, we take what we can"},{"s":116.54,"e":120.2,"text":"Bless this mouth, bless this man"},{"s":120.2,"e":123.42,"text":"St John’s plate, keep me alive"},{"s":123.42,"e":126.72,"text":"St John’s plate, I’m still inside"},{"s":126.72,"e":130.18,"text":"If love is real, let it come down here"},{"s":130.18,"e":133.64,"text":"(come down here) (come down here)"},{"s":134.38,"e":136.22,"text":"When the world gets loud"},{"s":136.22,"e":137.76,"text":"And the rent comes due"},{"s":137.76,"e":139.64,"text":"When the body folds"},{"s":139.64,"e":141.34,"text":"And the night eats through"},{"s":141.34,"e":142.96,"text":"I’ll stand in line"},{"s":142.96,"e":144.68,"text":"With my hands out too"},{"s":144.68,"e":146.38,"text":"Not above nobody"},{"s":146.6,"e":150.32,"text":"Just passing through"},{"s":150.78,"e":154.38,"text":"St John’s plate, keep me alive"},{"s":154.38,"e":157.76,"text":"St John’s plate, let me survive"},{"s":157.76,"e":161.3,"text":"Under God’s sky, we take what we can"},{"s":161.3,"e":164.58,"text":"Bless this mouth, bless this man"},{"s":164.58,"e":168.06,"text":"St John’s plate, keep me alive"},{"s":168.06,"e":171.28,"text":"St John’s plate, I’m still inside"},{"s":171.28,"e"